==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Zinco-
<hw>Zin"co-</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A combining form from
<xex>zinc</xex>; in chemistry, designating <xex>zinc</xex> as an element
of certain double compounds. Also used adjectively.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Zincode</ent>⟦br⟧
